{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"8bd1b3378e","title":"莫边府作战最大可能发生的危险在后方交通线","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"6aedd58b5a","index":0,"year":1954,"month":4,"day":28,"articleId":"8bd1b3378e"}],"tags":[{"id":"ae0a6697a5","name":"彭德怀","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji34","name":"毛泽东全集第34卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/34-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji34":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"8c0b32ecf3","type":"title","text":"奠边府作战最大可能发生的危险在后方交通线！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"8bd1b3378e"},{"id":"e58ec3cfb0","type":"paragraph","text":"彭德怀、黄克诚同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"8bd1b3378e"},{"id":"9f6466b5e9","type":"paragraph","text":"目前越南最大可能发生的危险，似乎不在莫边府以南，而在我军的后方交通线。如敌以两个伞兵营降落在我后方交通线上最拒要的地点，筑堡据守起来，整个交通将为之切断，如我军不能迅速弃灭此敌，矿日持久，莫边府我军即有被追撤退之可能。军委去电已估计到故有袭占交通线可能，但强调不够，并以之与郎勃拉邦方向并列。请你们再加考虑，叫越方迅调必要兵力位于适当地区，专门对付此种意外事变，以免莫边府作战功亏一等。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"8bd1b3378e"},{"id":"89e990e8df","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"8bd1b3378e"},{"id":"d19ba9a77a","type":"paragraph","text":"四月二十八","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"8bd1b3378e"},{"id":"7617c809d0","type":"paragraph","text":"[I]这是毛泽东写给中央人民政府人民革命军事委员会副主席彭德怀、人民革命军事委员会副总参课长兼总后方勤务部部长黄克诚的信。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"8bd1b3378e"}],"page":{"id":"bec4ee5068","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"8bd1b3378e","start":84,"end":84}}}},"__N_SSG":true}